{"tid":2085973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7 1 和理非強心針]陳皓桓:已知上訴委員會必定反對 但會照樣發起遊行","createTime":"2020-06-30T06:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:34:36.000Z","uid":17024,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dee42adaab85a13cbe49f84d0dc5ef5e545d16f","tid":2085973,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"熱門見到呢個post<br />\n一個近期離職&ldquo;黃&rdquo;督察 比前線手足一啲 提醒。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2085673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2085673</a><br />\n呢個係提醒緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">前線手足</span></span><br />\n而唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534871-20200630.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534871-20200630.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=447eaab9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534871-20200630.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=48e45950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534871-20200630.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wMpAHzBF3-o?t=983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwMpAHzBF3-o%3Ft%3D983&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=be8a9d76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wMpAHzBF3-o?t=983</a><br />\n唔知71之後仲會唔會有人夠膽舉辦/發起呢類遊行集會<br />\n而陳皓桓同一眾民主派議員都講到明 即使班狗反對 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日會照樣發起遊行</span></span><br />\n比世界睇多次香港人既團結<br />\n和理非會唔會一齊喺港島行個圈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">當最後一次看待啦</span></span>"},{"pid